                     <interp inst="t18090412-112-person988" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 7th of March, the prisoner pledged this watch for a guinea.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18090412-112-person989">
                  JOHN 
                  BURGES
